Step 1 : HTML footer template
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-content">
    <p>&copy; {{ year }} My Restaurant. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>


Step 2 : CSS Styling 
.site-footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 20px 0;
    text-align: center;
}

.site-footer .footer-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.site-footer a {
    color: #ffcc00;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.site-footer a:hocer {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

Step 3 : Link the CSS in base template
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{% static 'css/stylesheet.css' %}:>

Step 4 : TailwindCSS
<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-6">
  <div class="max-w-w6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm">&copy; {% now "Y" %} My Restaurant.All rights reserved. </p>
  </div>
</footer>

RESULT:::
> Dark background with white text.
> Center-aligned content.
> Links highlighted on hover.

